[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":474},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230124\u002F1507289668\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230124\u002F1507289668\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230124\u002F1507289668\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230124\u002F1507289668\u002F":450,"related:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230124\u002F1507289668\u002F":459},"\u002Fen\u002Fdocker\u002F2023\u002F01\u002F24\u002Fstep-by-step-docker-docker-hub\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":321,"date":433,"description":18,"extension":434,"lang":435,"meta":436,"navigation":437,"path":438,"readingMinutes":439,"seo":440,"standalone":441,"stem":442,"tags":443,"tldr":446,"updated":447,"url":448,"__hash__":449},"content\u002F一步步掌握基礎 Docker\u002F4-一步步掌握基礎-Docker-DockerHub？.md","(4)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - Docker Hub？","1507289668",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":421},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,46,49,60,69,76,79,82,86,89,142,146,152,158,165,168,266,269,272,278,300,303,307,312,328,331,337,341,344,358,361,367,370,399,402,405,409,414,417],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來要來額外認識 Docker 中很重要的一個東西，也就是 Docker Hub。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"docker-hub","Docker Hub",[16,24,25],{},"首先 Docker 本身有維護一個倉庫平台，也就是 Docker Hub，看到 Hub 有些人或許會馬上聯想到一個東西，也就是 GitHub 兩者雖然都是在做類似的事情，但還是稍微有一點點不同",[27,28,29,38],"ul",{},[30,31,32,33],"li",{},"GitHub\n",[27,34,35],{},[30,36,37],{},"用來託管程式碼的平台",[30,39,40,41],{},"Docker Hub\n",[27,42,43],{},[30,44,45],{},"用來託管 Docker Image 的平台",[16,47,48],{},"因此兩者還是有那麼一點點的不同。",[16,50,51,52,59],{},"當然 Docker Hub 也有分公私的儲存庫(Repository)，只是 Docker Hub 只有提供一個私有倉庫，而公有倉庫則是無限，這一點可以稍微注意一下，如果想知道更多詳細的細節，你可以到 ",[53,54,58],"a",{"href":55,"rel":56},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.docker.com\u002Fpricing\u002F",[57],"nofollow","Docker 付款頁面","查看。",[16,61,62,63,68],{},"那麼如果你還沒有註冊 Docker Hub 平台的帳號的話，我會建議你",[53,64,67],{"href":65,"rel":66},"https:\u002F\u002Fhub.docker.com\u002Fsignup",[57],"點此連結","開始註冊，註冊的細節我就不介紹了，那麼假設你已經註冊完畢，並且也登入了，那麼你當前畫面可能是如下方所示",[16,70,71],{},[72,73],"img",{"alt":74,"src":75},"Docker","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002F7rMbxbf.png",[16,77,78],{},"只要你畫面跟上面雷同，那麼就代表你帳號也註冊並且成功登入。",[16,80,81],{},"（畫面有可能隨著 Docker 版本更新而不同，但大致上的概念是一樣的。）",[12,83,85],{"id":84},"docker-hub-指令操作","Docker Hub 指令操作",[16,87,88],{},"接著讓我們來認識一些基本的 Docker Hub 指令操作，首先有幾個指令你必須了解分別是",[27,90,91,102,112,122,132],{},[30,92,93,97],{},[94,95,96],"code",{},"docker login",[27,98,99],{},[30,100,101],{},"登入 Docker Hub",[30,103,104,107],{},[94,105,106],{},"docker logout",[27,108,109],{},[30,110,111],{},"登出 Docker Hub",[30,113,114,117],{},[94,115,116],{},"docker search",[27,118,119],{},[30,120,121],{},"搜尋 Docker Hub 上的 Image",[30,123,124,127],{},[94,125,126],{},"docker pull",[27,128,129],{},[30,130,131],{},"從 Docker Hub 上拉取 Image",[30,133,134,137],{},[94,135,136],{},"docker push",[27,138,139],{},[30,140,141],{},"將 Image 推送到 Docker Hub",[143,144,101],"h3",{"id":145},"登入-docker-hub",[16,147,148,149,151],{},"首先這邊先在終端機內輸入 ",[94,150,96],{},"，輸入後他會要求你輸入你的 Docker Hub 使用者名稱與密碼",[16,153,154],{},[72,155],{"alt":156,"src":157},"login","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FeZS3Wzo.png",[16,159,160,161,164],{},"（如果出現「",[94,162,163],{},"Error response from daemon: Get \"https:\u002F\u002Fregistry-1.docker.io\u002Fv2\u002F\": unauthorized: incorrect username or password","」代表你帳號或密碼錯誤唷。）",[16,166,167],{},"登入成功後，基本上你會看到以下訊息",[169,170,175],"pre",{"className":171,"code":172,"language":173,"meta":174,"style":174},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","Logging in with your password grants your terminal complete access to your account.\nFor better security, log in with a limited-privilege personal access token. Learn more at https:\u002F\u002Fdocs.docker.com\u002Fgo\u002Faccess-tokens\u002F\n","bash","",[94,176,177,221],{"__ignoreMap":174},[178,179,182,186,190,193,196,199,202,204,207,210,213,216,218],"span",{"class":180,"line":181},"line",1,[178,183,185],{"class":184},"s_sBn","Logging",[178,187,189],{"class":188},"sTRMh"," in",[178,191,192],{"class":188}," with",[178,194,195],{"class":188}," your",[178,197,198],{"class":188}," password",[178,200,201],{"class":188}," grants",[178,203,195],{"class":188},[178,205,206],{"class":188}," terminal",[178,208,209],{"class":188}," complete",[178,211,212],{"class":188}," access",[178,214,215],{"class":188}," to",[178,217,195],{"class":188},[178,219,220],{"class":188}," account.\n",[178,222,224,227,230,233,236,238,240,243,246,249,251,254,257,260,263],{"class":180,"line":223},2,[178,225,226],{"class":184},"For",[178,228,229],{"class":188}," better",[178,231,232],{"class":188}," security,",[178,234,235],{"class":188}," log",[178,237,189],{"class":188},[178,239,192],{"class":188},[178,241,242],{"class":188}," a",[178,244,245],{"class":188}," limited-privilege",[178,247,248],{"class":188}," personal",[178,250,212],{"class":188},[178,252,253],{"class":188}," token.",[178,255,256],{"class":188}," Learn",[178,258,259],{"class":188}," more",[178,261,262],{"class":188}," at",[178,264,265],{"class":188}," https:\u002F\u002Fdocs.docker.com\u002Fgo\u002Faccess-tokens\u002F\n",[16,267,268],{},"這樣子就代表你成功登入囉。",[143,270,111],{"id":271},"登出-docker-hub",[16,273,274,275,277],{},"登出相對比較少在使用，除非是暫時用的不是是自己電腦，不然其實 ",[94,276,106],{}," 這個指令的使用機會很低，當你在終端機輸入之後，你會得到以下訊息",[169,279,281],{"className":171,"code":280,"language":173,"meta":174,"style":174},"Removing login credentials for https:\u002F\u002Findex.docker.io\u002Fv1\u002F\n",[94,282,283],{"__ignoreMap":174},[178,284,285,288,291,294,297],{"class":180,"line":181},[178,286,287],{"class":184},"Removing",[178,289,290],{"class":188}," login",[178,292,293],{"class":188}," credentials",[178,295,296],{"class":188}," for",[178,298,299],{"class":188}," https:\u002F\u002Findex.docker.io\u002Fv1\u002F\n",[16,301,302],{},"代表著原本儲存於你電腦內的登入憑證已經被刪除了。",[143,304,306],{"id":305},"搜尋-docker-image","搜尋 Docker Image",[16,308,309,311],{},[94,310,116],{}," 其實非常簡單，只需要在後面補上你想要搜尋的 Image 名稱，例如我想搜尋 Node.js 那麼就要輸入以下指令",[169,313,315],{"className":171,"code":314,"language":173,"meta":174,"style":174},"docker search node\n",[94,316,317],{"__ignoreMap":174},[178,318,319,322,325],{"class":180,"line":181},[178,320,321],{"class":184},"docker",[178,323,324],{"class":188}," search",[178,326,327],{"class":188}," node\n",[16,329,330],{},"接著你就會看到一大推跟 Node 有關的 Image",[16,332,333],{},[72,334],{"alt":335,"src":336},"Image List","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FdKwSAkz.png",[143,338,340],{"id":339},"拉取-docker-image","拉取 Docker Image",[16,342,343],{},"那麼假設我想要拉取剛剛搜尋到的 Node.js Image，以 Node.js 為例，就要輸入以下指令",[169,345,347],{"className":171,"code":346,"language":173,"meta":174,"style":174},"docker pull node\n",[94,348,349],{"__ignoreMap":174},[178,350,351,353,356],{"class":180,"line":181},[178,352,321],{"class":184},[178,354,355],{"class":188}," pull",[178,357,327],{"class":188},[16,359,360],{},"接著你就會看到以下畫面",[16,362,363],{},[72,364],{"alt":365,"src":366},"pull","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FEIFxRdN.png",[16,368,369],{},"而這個過程會需要等待一下，當出現以下訊息",[169,371,373],{"className":171,"code":372,"language":173,"meta":174,"style":174},"Status: Downloaded newer image for node:latest\ndocker.io\u002Flibrary\u002Fnode:latest\n",[94,374,375,394],{"__ignoreMap":174},[178,376,377,380,383,386,389,391],{"class":180,"line":181},[178,378,379],{"class":184},"Status:",[178,381,382],{"class":188}," Downloaded",[178,384,385],{"class":188}," newer",[178,387,388],{"class":188}," image",[178,390,296],{"class":188},[178,392,393],{"class":188}," node:latest\n",[178,395,396],{"class":180,"line":223},[178,397,398],{"class":184},"docker.io\u002Flibrary\u002Fnode:latest\n",[16,400,401],{},"就代表這個 Node.js 的 Image 已經被拉取下來到你的電腦內了。",[16,403,404],{},"那該怎麼使用呢？這一個我們後面再來聊。",[143,406,408],{"id":407},"推送-docker-image","推送 Docker Image",[16,410,411,413],{},[94,412,136],{}," 相對簡單很多，就是將你封裝的 Image 給推到 Docker Hub 上，而這部分我們後續會再來介紹，你先知道這個指令就好。",[16,415,416],{},"以上差不多是我們在 Docker Hub 上的基本指令唷~",[418,419,420],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":174,"searchDepth":223,"depth":223,"links":422},[423,424,425],{"id":14,"depth":223,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":223,"text":22},{"id":84,"depth":223,"text":85,"children":426},[427,429,430,431,432],{"id":145,"depth":428,"text":101},3,{"id":271,"depth":428,"text":111},{"id":305,"depth":428,"text":306},{"id":339,"depth":428,"text":340},{"id":407,"depth":428,"text":408},"2023-01-24 14:36:00","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fdocker\u002F4-docker-dockerhub","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"一步步掌握基礎 Docker\u002F4-一步步掌握基礎-Docker-DockerHub？",[321,444,22,445],"一步步掌握基礎 Docker","Docker Image",null,"2023-02-13 15:30:00","\u002Fdocker\u002F20230124\u002F1507289668\u002F","OCOtavfk1fRX314lCqH9BNvMrLo_iRE9eHdL1tWlSmU",{"newer":451,"older":455},{"url":452,"title":453,"date":454},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230125\u002F2499755737\u002F","(5)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - Docker 常見容器指令","2023-01-25 20:20:00",{"url":456,"title":457,"date":458},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230123\u002F2896707023\u002F","(3)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - 小試身手","2023-01-23 21:20:00",[460,465,470],{"url":461,"title":462,"date":463,"readingMinutes":464},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20241219\u002F2070727594\u002F","如何將 Vite+Vue 封裝到 Docker 並運行？","2024-12-19 16:36:18","3",{"url":466,"title":467,"date":468,"readingMinutes":469},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F1926467390\u002F","(11)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - 目錄","2023-01-29 15:22:19","1",{"url":471,"title":472,"date":473,"readingMinutes":469},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F345996692\u002F","(10)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - Docker GUI","2023-01-29 15:20:19",1784012764495]